@Author(value={"Julian Fleischer","Andre Zoufahl","David Bialik"})
public class Admin
extends FriggModule<RelationManager>

A module providing administrative tasks.

The sole purpose of this module is to show option-panes and forms, the actual logic is contained in UserMgmt, ImportExport, ...
